shows, Yorke said that:\\n\\n> It can be cool sometimes, but other times I want to stop halfway through and be like, \'Nah, this isn\'t happening\'.\",\"body\":{\"markdown\":\"Thom Yorke [said](http://www.bbc.co.uk/musictv/popontrial/decades/index.shtml?d=90s&a=hide&t=show&c=show&n=33&q=hide&m=hide&) that the song is trying: \\n\\n> to assert a sexual persona and on the other hand trying desperately to negate it.\\n\\n[Explaining](https://faroutmagazine.co.uk/radiohead-unwanted-hit-creep-story-behind-the-song/) why it\'s rarely played at their live shows, Yorke said that:\\n\\n> It can be cool sometimes, but other times I want to stop halfway through and be like, \'Nah, this isn\'t happening\'.\",\"html\":\"<p>Thom Yorke <a href=\\\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/musictv/popontrial/decades/index.shtml?d=90s&amp;a=hide&amp;t=show&amp;c=show&amp;n=33&amp;q=hide&amp;m=hide&amp;\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">said<\/a> that the song is trying:<\/p>\\n\\n<blockquote><p>to assert a sexual persona and on the other hand trying desperately to negate it.<\/p><\/blockquote>\\n\\n<p><a href=\\\"https://faroutmagazine.co.uk/radiohead-unwanted-hit-creep-story-behind-the-song/\\\" rel=\\\"noopener nofollow\\\">Explaining<\/a> why it’s rarely played at their live shows, Yorke said that:<\/p>\\n\\n<blockquote><p>It can be cool sometimes, but other times I want to stop halfway through and be like, ‘Nah, this isn’t happening’.<\/p><\/blockquote>\"},\"type\":\"answer\"}},\"questions\":{\"108764\":{\"defaultQuestion\":{\"id\":\"artist_comment:song:109096\",\"answerPrefix\":null},\"author\":3187763,\"answer\":129457,\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"vote\":null},\"iqByAction\":{},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"vote\",\"add_answer\",\"update_answer_source\",\"update\",\"archive\",\"pin\",\"unpin\",\"move\",\"moderate\",\"add_verified_answer\",\"view_qa_page\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"votesTotal\":0,\"url\":\"https://genius.com/Radiohead-creep-lyrics/questions/108764\",\"state\":\"pinned\",\